# Bloggy — Blog & News Feed Platform

> A responsive blog platform with category filtering, 
> search, dark/light theme, and a dynamic editorial layout.

🔗 **Live demo:** [https://blog-app-flax-gamma.vercel.app/]

---

## Overview

Bloggy is a full-featured blog and news feed UI built to 
simulate a real editorial platform across six content 
categories — Technology, Design, Business, Culture, 
Science, and Health.

---

## Features

- **Category filtering** — filter by Technology, Design, 
  Business, Culture, Science, Health
- **Search** — live search across article titles 
  and content
- **Dark and light theme** — toggle with 
  persistent preference
- **Editorial layout** — featured hero, trending section, 
  most-read sidebar
- **Dynamic sections** — articles update based on active 
  filter and search query
- **Fully responsive**

---

