## Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Smartbabbe/[blog-app]
cd [blog-app]
npm install
npm run dev
```

---

## Key Implementation Details

- Article data typed as TypeScript objects with category, 
  tags, read time, and author fields
- Search filters against both title and body content 
  using Array.filter
- Theme toggle using useState with Tailwind dark: 
  variant classes
- Trending and most-read sections derived dynamically 
  from the same data source

